COUNTY OF BEXAR
STATE OF TEXAS
A.
Claimant:
City of San Antonio
Mailing Address:
P.O. Box 839966, San Antonio, TX 78283-3966
City of San Antonio claims a mortgage lien on the following real property and improvements in the City of
San Antonio, County of Bexar, Texas:
1410 W. Gramercy Place, San Antonio, Texas 78201, more particularly described as Lot 10, Block 55, New
City Block 2749, Keystone Park, in the City of San Antonio, Bexar County, Texas, according to plat thereof
recorded in Volume 105, Page 156, of the Deed and Plat Records of Bexar County, Texas (the "Property").
B.
Said claim is for the sum of Fifteen Thousand and 00/100 Dollars ($15,000.00), which is due and
unpaid to Claimant by Lorenzo Vela ("Debtor") for consideration in a contractual agreement.
C.
Claimant is a purchase money lender for the Property. Claimant's claim hereunder is subordinate
only to the first lien on the Property created by that certain Deed of Trust executed by and between Debtor
and American Pacific Mortgage Corp ., in the original principal amount of One Hundred Sixty-One
Thousand Five Hundred and 00/100 Dollars ($161,500.00).
